Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:09.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:20.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.22,0:00:38.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:46.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:53.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:59.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:06.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:14.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:20.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:28.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:59.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Door to a New World
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've never seen\Nsuch insubordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:28.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is why I was against\Ndisbanding Rubor and Caput!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,We cannot afford to rely\Nsolely on Chor Tempest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:36.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Gather all our troops and Similes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:39.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,The patrol Similes and the\Ncruise Similes. I want them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:40.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:42.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:47.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Conflict will not\Nbring about a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:27.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,I told you not to do that!\NStop playing with the Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:30.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? So how come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:31.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:33.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:36.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:41.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:44.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's making a sound,\Nlike it's humming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're right!\NIt's humming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:52.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,It sounds like a whistle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:54.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,You too, Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:05.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can hear a humming sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:11.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:45.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.27,0:04:48.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,So that day has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:52.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please give us a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:57.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you mind waiting\Nuntil we've finished eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:05.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have negotiations\Nbroken down then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:09.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia is the symbol\Nof Simulacrum Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:12.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Undoubtedly it is to our\Nsuperiors' advantage that she...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,...maintain her current silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:18.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, should Onasia\Ndecide to make a move...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:21.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,I certainly don't enjoy conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:23.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:26.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bringing Onasia here\Nat a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:30.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just don't understand what the\Nhigh priestess could be thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:31.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:32.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Suppose I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:33.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Suppose I...\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:36.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:59.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Taking off in the Simouns\Nwithout authorization...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:01.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is an unprecedented infraction!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:04.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where is your sense\Nof responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:05.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:08.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do we recognize that we're Simoun\Nsibyllae and take pride in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:12.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I would say that's true\Nof each and every one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that all you have to say to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,If so, please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:31.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,You little brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:41.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:45.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vura...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:49.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,And Roatreamon and Alty, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just as we thought, Paraietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,You couldn't sleep either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:56.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neither could we.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:00.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:07.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, is the whole gang here then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:41.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,We shall send Onasia\Nback on the Messis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:44.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril, Sibylla Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:48.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,May I ask you to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:54.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you not want to know more\Nabout that different world?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:00.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Will you take me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:01.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, we cannot go in\Nsuch great numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:07.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:27.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:31.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:33.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I'd call it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:37.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a little bitter, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:41.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,And it's also a little bit sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it's not that\NI don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:46.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:48.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I can finish it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:52.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I don't know..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:53.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:56.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've stopped saying\Nthat all the time, Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:58.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:08:59.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:03.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that if you really think about it,\Nthere's nothing you can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:04.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:06.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:11.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,The more I think about\Nsomething, the more lost I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:22.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, let's finish eating,\Nand then we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:23.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:29.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,The high priestess\Nhas ordered us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:37.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to make this as smooth\Na flight as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:38.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:41.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder where we're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:55.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:56.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:10:00.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia-sama is at rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:01.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:25.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did she bring up\Nthe "different world"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:28.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,That high priestess...\NThere's something about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:31.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure, the military councilor's\Nan annoying old man too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:32.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but that high priestess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:39.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:41.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:43.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they're so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't treat me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,War makes things that\Nshould be obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:55.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,...so very hard\Nto see, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:03.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is something\Nyou wish to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:12.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,You told me that you\Ncould hear Mamina's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:14.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,So... what about my comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:20.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have their souls been released?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:27.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,The one who really\Nwishes to be released...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:29.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is you yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:36.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,By placing yourself at the\Nbrink of your comrades' deaths...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:40.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,...you are actually trying to flee\Nas far as possible from those deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:54.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onasia-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:56.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,We seem to have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:44.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why the Ruins?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:54.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,There it goes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:57.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,The door to a new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:13:00.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,The melody played\Nby that music box...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:05.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,...as well as the unintended destination\Nof those who lost their lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:06.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:08.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,This was once the training\Nground for Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:13.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Dextra?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:15.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:18.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,...that was the chor your own\Ngrandfather served as regina for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:21.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Grandpa... a regina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:37.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:38.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:40.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,What day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:45.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,On the Messis...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:50.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,It all came surging back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:54.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,The moment I looked into\Nthe helical motors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:56.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was as if I was seeing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:57.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Somebody's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:13:59.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,The memory of something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:04.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,What you see there is\Nnothing but a helix.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:08.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,As it turns out, the only thing\Nwe're capable of understanding is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:29.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:40.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,And then we became enthralled\Nwith Ri Majons... and the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:44.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,But that was because we had nothing\Nbut the Simouns to cling to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:45.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:48.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,If the Simouns had never\Nexisted in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:51.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or even if they had existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:54.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but no one ever\Ndiscovered how to use them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,...then what would have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:02.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:04.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:18.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,We brought them here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,We brought them here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:21.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:42.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Long, long ago, there was a\Ncivilization far superior to ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:47.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,And it is said that the Simouns\Nwere in existence at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,But after a succession\Nof wars broke out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:53.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the country was left in ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:56.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,And once all of the lands\Nwere rendered worthless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,...there was no longer\Nany reason to wage war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:01.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,The starving multitudes no\Nlonger needed the Simouns...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:03.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and eventually they\Nforgot how to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:06.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,The people...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:09.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,...had no choice but to wait for\Ncertain destruction at nature's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was then that something\Nbroke through the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:21.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and a Simoun arrived\Nfrom a different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:25.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,On board that Simoun\Nwere two children of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,These young girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:33.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,These young girls announced\Nthemselves as "Simoun sibyllae."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:36.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,They then shared the secret\Nof the Emerald Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:40.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:41.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,To a different world...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:46.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, that which transports one to a\Ndifferent time, the ultimate Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:50.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is a divine gift.\NA magnificent "if."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,What if during that era...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:58.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they had told the people\Nthat another war was coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,If the Simouns hadn't existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:05.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,...then I might never\Nhave existed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:07.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,If, during that era...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:10.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they found a way to convince the\Npeople of the need for Simouns...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:18.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if I'd never existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:20.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,...then this pain never\Nwould've existed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:24.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,This era so full of hardship\Nand strife might be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:27.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,To transcend time and space...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:30.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and offer this\N"if" to some other era.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:33.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,That is precisely the purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:36.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,...of the Simouns and\Nof the Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:38.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Transcend time and space?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:40.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable... How could that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:44.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! Then what about this\NChor Dextra you say my grandpa led?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Dextra...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:50.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was created for the sole purpose\Nof completing the Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:54.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Someone you know very well was\Nalso a former member of this chor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:55.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:58.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:02.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,She is the last surviving\Nmember of Chor Dextra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:07.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:09.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:12.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I had the misfortune to find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:22.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,That everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:25.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,That everything that\Nhappened started with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:45.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:46.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:49.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought about what\Nyou just said, Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:52.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know, if the Simouns\Nhad never existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they hadn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:56.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:00.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then I never would've met\Neveryone in Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:02.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,And, Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:05.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I never would've met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:16.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:17.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:18.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.98,0:19:20.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:21.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because it hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,What else...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:26.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:30.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you're happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:32.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:34.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:39.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:43.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean go without\Nknowing where again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:44.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:45.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do know where.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:12.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Under the blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:17.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Beyond the white clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:23.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's as blue as a tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:28.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,As white as a lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:34.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the pitch-black darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:40.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,The light of a red flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:49.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra most likely\Ncompleted the Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:50.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:52.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,She is alive in another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.34,0:20:59.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra and Sibylla\NRimone are both alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am certain that they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:02.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:05.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:07.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:11.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,...does that mean that Amuria\Nmay also be alive somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:19.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon was a\Ndivine gift. Our only hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:23.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether it will take us into the\Nfuture or back into the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:25.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,That is not for us to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:27.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:31.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it is by the will of the gods of\NTempus Spatium that the Simouns exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:35.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the gods cannot be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:41.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am positive that they will\Nopen the door to the correct era.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:43.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:44.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:47.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I would like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:49.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,...entrust this task to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:52.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:02.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.91,0:22:08.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,You say it's a Simoun\Nfrom the Arcus Niger?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:09.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Military councilor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.61,0:22:11.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:14.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Arcus Niger...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:16.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was shot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:18.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:22.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seven o'clock! Five ancient\NSimouns approaching fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:23.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:47.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:52.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.12,0:22:59.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.20,0:23:06.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:19.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to get closer to you.\NI want to feel your pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:24.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.86,0:23:28.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.83,0:23:32.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.86,0:23:38.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.74,0:23:44.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the\Nsky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:47.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.71,0:23:53.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.38,0:23:59.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:06.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.03,0:24:06.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued\NThe Shoukoku-Plumbum highlands allied forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.56,0:24:08.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Shoukoku-Plumbum highlands allied forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.57,0:24:10.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,...have begun their\Ninvasion of Kyuukoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.47,0:24:12.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and the attacks are\Nincreasing by the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.07,0:24:15.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.44,0:24:16.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sortie
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.14,0:24:17.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sortie\NSortie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.67,0:24:19.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sortie
